Package: OUTRIDER
Type: Package
Title: OUTRIDER - OUTlier RNA-Seq fInDER
Version: 0.99.4
Date: 2018-02-22
Maintainer: Christian Mertes <mertes@in.tum.de>
Description: Identification of aberrent gene expression in RNA-seq data.
    OUTRIDER finds expression outliers by fitting an Negative-Binomial 
    distribution per gene over all read counts and computing P-values 
    for each of them. Further OUTRIDER provides useful plotting 
    function to visualize the results.
Author: Felix Brechtmann, Agne Matuseviciute, Christian Mertes,
    Vicente Yepez, Julien Gagneur
